724905f-a.title: Manhattan: York Avenue - 74th Street
724905f-a.text:
York Ave (Avenue A), west side, north from and including Eaat
74th Street. Shown at the N.W. corner of Eaat 74th Street is an
itinerant circus.
September 25, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
